  10 Feb 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  pulseaudio-0.9.22-r2.ebuild, pulseaudio-0.9.22.ebuild,
  pulseaudio-0.9.23-r1.ebuild, pulseaudio-1.1-r1.ebuild, pulseaudio-1.1.ebuild,
  pulseaudio-9999.ebuild:
