  29 Dec 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -files/pulseaudio-0.9.6-build.patch, -pulseaudio-0.9.6-r1.ebuild,
  -pulseaudio-0.9.8-r2.ebuild, -pulseaudio-0.9.8-r3.ebuild:
  Cleanup old versions.

